  "description": "The dataset is a tab-deliminted text file with genotyping information for\n a diploid potato progeny population derived from a cross of diploid potato\n clones 12120-03 X 07506-01. The SolCap 8303 Infinium Chip was used for SNP\n genotyping.  It was originally generated for study on genetic\n mapping of Verticillium wilt resistance.  The data was used again\n for analysis of segregation distortion in the most recent\n manuscript.  ",
